{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5ea4bb920a","title":"北京市中级人民法院刑事关于奚纹右派等问题再审判决书","origin":"根据文件翻印件打印。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"68a7485ec0","index":0,"year":1979,"month":5,"day":11,"articleId":"5ea4bb920a"}],"tags":[{"id":"aa9434abe4","name":"北京文革","type":"人物"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"2e6890fe4c","type":"title","text":"北京市中级人民法院刑事关于奚纹右派等问题再审判决书","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"},{"id":"9eef5a67b5","type":"paragraph","text":"申诉人（原审被告）：奚纹，（奚玉梅），女，42岁，上海市人，原系中央戏剧学院表演系学生，共青团员。1957年被划为右派分子，开除团籍，1958年10月6日经本院以反革命罪判处有期徒刑10年，剥夺政治权利4年。1967年11月14日刑满释放。现在山西省阳泉矿务局荫营煤矿当工人。","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"},{"id":"d1cdd85666","type":"paragraph","text":"现奚纹对本院（58）反字第1290号判决不服，提出申诉，要求重新审理。","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"},{"id":"42fbc130ca","type":"paragraph","text":"经本院再审查明：奚纹的右派问题系错划，其原所在单位已复查改正；关于与外国人乱搞男女关系及泄漏国内情况问题是违法犯罪的，鉴于已经多年改造可从宽处理。但原判以犯反革命罪论不当，应予以纠正。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"},{"id":"fc4c59e222","type":"paragraph","text":"据此，判决如下：","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"},{"id":"51958aefc4","type":"paragraph","text":"一、撤销本院（58）反字第1290号判决；","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"},{"id":"7fdbfbae01","type":"paragraph","text":"二、对奚纹不予刑事处分。","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"},{"id":"1af2bb41c5","type":"paragraph","text":"如不服本判决，可于接到判决之次日起十天内，向本院提出上诉状及付本，上诉于北京市高级人民法院。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"},{"id":"71ca7928e6","type":"paragraph","text":" 1979年5月11日","index":8,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a"}],"page":{"id":"37ec0a665c","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5ea4bb920a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}